{"tid":2104492,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個唔明佢做乜嘅emoji","createTime":"2020-07-12T04:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T14:17:31.000Z","uid":192075,"like":11,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d5de0d45ff8f5c56b0b3382522b8159ed1e5c84c","tid":2104492,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"🥴<br />\n<br />\n呢個emoji其實代表咩意思？<br />\n<br />\n入面個情感實在唔簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢又好似想同我單眼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個咀仔又唔知點解暗爽緊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果眼夾埋個咀一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至散發出一種佢搭緊一架爆曬棚嘅巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而自己只可以罰企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伴隨住架車前後上下嘅震盪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將所有嘅掙扎集中係個肛門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍屎忍到去自我界限嘅一種氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講咁多個emoji<br />\n一定無一個夠呢個複雜同戲劇性<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"2fdbb6e90b353dbcce93d3ecc3cc2327a311b3b7","tid":2104492,"uid":13065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"😦😦😦"},{"pid":"e6403d6ab9cb77d0eb43b94d862f5fd3359dd41e","tid":2104492,"uid":192075,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"2fdbb6e90b353dbcce93d3ecc3cc2327a311b3b7","tid":2104492,"uid":13065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"😦😦😦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"😧😧😧<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n有堂眉同無堂眉都兩個emoji"},{"pid":"ec82520aa673b3cea6d3d03dcd7d1dbd0308cad7","tid":2104492,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"🇨🇳"},{"pid":"0c79e99353bf68d5a2b6c8869fd5c7338c0ef7c6","tid":2104492